reviewText: On a bigger screen this seems to be a bit grainy. I have a 65" and it doest look that good.

In this tape i have found that the picture looked very bad. It is obvious that the maker simply put a camera on the side of a fish take and filmed some fish on hopes of making a quick buck by selling. I would not recomend this tape to anyone looking for anything nice, but simply as a tape to buy if you just want to look at a fishtank
